          "email": "quentin.bouget@cea.fr",
          "date": "2017-12-12 15:29:02.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-10344 tests: fix atime in sanity-hsm/test_24a",
        "message": "LU-10344 tests: fix atime in sanity-hsm/test_24a\n\ntest_24a requires a file for which atime < {mtime, ctime}\n\nPreviously, the test would create the file, sleep 1 second and\nappend an empty string to the file. This was unreliable and\nsometimes, mtime and ctime would remain the same.\n\nNow, the test uses \"touch -ad yesterday $file\" to rewind the atime.\n\nSigned-off-by: Quentin Bouget <quentin.bouget@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I1b9a71e3e0e5312ac53c93e6c8b1db189df1e96f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
